<html xmlns:t="http://tapestry.apache.org/schema/tapestry_5_1_0.xsd">

<head>
    <title>N2WTextFieldDemo1</title>


    <style type="text/css">
        span.numberToWord {
            font-size: 12pt;
            font-style: italic;
            color: blue;
        }

        span.error {
            font-size: 18pt;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: red;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<h1>N2WTextFieldDemo1</h1>

A demo on the component N2WTextField.

<br/><br/>
Test : css style for word output and error message. <br/><br/>

<form t:id="myForm" t:type="form">
    Please enter a number: <input t:type="lombok/n2wTextField" type="input" value="myNumber"
                                  wordCSS="literal:numberToWord" errorCSS="literal:error"
                                  maxlength="12"/> <br/>


</form>

</body>
</html>

